text: Nigel Keith Anthony Standish Vaz, known as Keith Vaz, was born 26 November 1956 in Aden, Yemen to Indian parents. He moved to Twickenham, London during his childhood. He was a MP for Leicester South. In 2007, Vaz was diagnosed with Type 2 diabetes.May and Vaz have diabetes == References == Category:1956 births Category:Living people Category:Labour Party (UK) MPs Category:Members of the British House of Commons for English constituencies Category:Politicians from London
